This project is a maintained derivative of m1heng/clawdbot-feishu and includes
backported changes from the bundled Feishu extension shipped in openclaw/openclaw.

Original upstreams:
- https://github.com/m1heng/clawdbot-feishu
- https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw

This branch additionally carries local changes for:
- multi-account routing
- milestoneContext / group-summary injection
- task and sheet tool registration
- long-markdown delivery tuning
- webhook hardening and persistent dedup backports

